import React, { useRef } from 'react'; export default function Prompts(props) { return (

{props.title}

  • Have you ever had a dream that felt like it came true in real life?
  • If you could live in any era throughout history, which one would you choose and why?
  • What's the craziest adventure you've ever been on?
  • If you could only eat one meal for the rest of your life, what would it be?
  • What's the most interesting thing you've ever witnessed in public?
  • If you could swap lives with any person for a week, who would you choose and why?
  • If you could have dinner with any historical figure, who would it be and why?
  • What's the most meaningful gift you've ever received?
  • What's something you've always wanted to learn or try but haven't yet?
  • What's the best concert or live performance you've ever attended?
  • What's something you've always wanted to do but haven't had the opportunity yet?
  • What's the most interesting place you've ever visited and why was it memorable?
  • What's the best piece of advice you've ever received?
  • What's the most challenging thing you've ever done and how did you overcome it?
  • Do you have a favorite childhood toy or keepsake? If so, what is it and why is it special to you?
  • What's your favorite way to celebrate special occasions?
  • What's your favorite childhood book or movie and why?
  • What's your favorite thing about yourself and why?
  • What's your dream job or career?
  • If you could have any animal as a pet, what would it be and why?
  • What's your favorite way to relax or de-stress after a long day?
  • Do you have any favorite traditions or memories?
  • What's your favorite way to pamper or treat yourself?
  • If you could have a conversation with your younger self, what advice would you give?
  • What's a small act of kindness that someone has done for you that you still remember to this day?
  • What's something that you're passionate about that not many people know about?
  • What's something that always puts a smile on your face?
  • Do you have any favorite quotes from books, movies, or speeches?
  • How do you handle stress or difficult situations?
  • What is your favorite outfit?
  • What is your favorite dessert?
  • Have you ever had a near-death experience? If so, what was it like?
  • Where is your favorite place to travel?
  • Do you have a favorite quote or mantra that you live by?
  • What's your favorite type of snack?
  • Do you prefer city life or rural living, and why?
  • What's the most valuable lesson you've learned from a mistake or failure?
  • What's your favorite way to relax and unwind?
  • If you could have any animal as a pet, what would it be and why?
  • Do you enjoy sports, and if so, which ones?
  • What is your favorite personality trait about your significant other?
  • What's something that always puts a smile on your face?
  • What's the best gift you've ever given to someone?
  • Tell me about your relationship with your siblings growing up? Who was your favorite?
  • If you could have any superpower, what would it be and why?
  • If you could swap lives with any person for a week, who would you choose and why?
  • Do you have any hobbies or special talents?
  • Do you have any phobias or fears?
  • Do you have a favorite childhood game or activity?
  • What's your favorite way to spend a lazy day?
  • Who has been the most influential/ inspirational person in your life?
  • Do you have a favorite musical artist or band? If so, who are they and why do you like them?
); }
